OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStaying dry and warm in the
OL,6,Fwest with prolonged sunny spells.
OL,7,FCooler and cloudier in the northeast
OL,8,Fwith perhaps the odd spot of rain.
OL,9,FGentle northwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some evening
OL,12,Fsunshine, turning cloudier at times
OL,13,Fduring the night and a gentle
OL,14,Fnortherly winds, perhaps some patchy
OL,15,Frain for the north and the Hebrides by
OL,16,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
