OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy with some light rain
OL,6,Ffor the Hebrides and far north
OL,7,Fotherwise dry with some bright spells.
OL,8,FA few afternoon showers developing in
OL,9,Fthe light westerly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,12,Fcloudy and showery start to the the
OL,13,Fnew week but conditions improving
OL,14,Flater on Monday. Light winds and a mix
OL,15,Fof cloud and brighter spells
OL,16,Fcontinuing towards mid week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
